<h2 id="capo-1st-fret-optional">Capo 1st Fret (optional)</h2>

<p>If you want to play along with the Johnny Cash recorded versions of this song, youâ€™ll need to add a capo to the 1st fret (and use the chords shown above). Otherwise, this is by no means required! You can play without a capo using the notation above and it will sound just fine â€“ youâ€™ll simply in a different key (which is fine).</p>

